snippet: Winslow took exception when Cromartie, a cornerback, put his teammate Dee Milliner on the spot during an interview Tuesday.
abstract: Former New York Jets tight end Kellen Winslow Jr blasts Jets cornerback Antonio Cromartie on Twitter for putting his teammate Dee Milliner on spot during interview.
lead_paragraph: Winslow took exception when Cromartie, a cornerback, put his teammate Dee Milliner on the spot during an interview Tuesday.

headline.main: Kellen Winslow Jr. and Antonio Cromartie Feud on Twitter
